{
"#name"
:
{
"x"
:
"x-cmd core function"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x <subcommand> [<subcommand>...]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"X-CMD 是一个 POSIX shell 工具箱：300+ 模块，500+ 可移植软件包，1200+ 软件安装配方。"
,
"en"
:
"X-CMD is a POSIX shell toolkit: 300+ modules, 500+ portable packages, 1200+ software installation recipes."
}
,
